Virat Kohli is an Indian Cricketer and Former Indian team captain. 
This dataset contains details about his all centuries. There are two separate files for international and domestic centuries.
The dataset attempts to answer questions like:
What is the total number of centuries Kohli has scored according to the formats
What is his average strike rate
His lowest and highest score, batting average and dot ball percentage
What is his optimal batting position 
The country wise classification of his centuries
His IPL Performance
Which Venue and Nation he performs the best at?
How is his home vs away performance
What is the correlation between Kohli's performance and results for INDIAN Cricket team?
